  • public class LightSensitivity
extends SightImpairment
    Ontological representation of light sensitivity impairment. Methods included in this class are the mandatory ones for representing an ontological concept in Java classes for uAAL. Usually it includes getters and setters for most of its properties.
    Author:
    mtazari, Carsten Stockloew
